# ADR Governance

Technology decisions may change ONLY through a new or superseding ADR in `docs/adr/`.

Before adding or changing dependencies in `pyproject.toml` or `package.json`:

1. Verify an accepted ADR authorizes the technology
2. If no ADR exists: stop implementation and create an ADR proposal first
3. Update `docs/12-technology-decisions-and-adr-index.md` when ADR is accepted

## Normative stack (reference)

See `docs/12-technology-decisions-and-adr-index.md` — do not substitute components independently.
